  "texts": [
    "However, when it comes to output (granular predictions), it is unclear whether a technological solution can resolve the fundamental trade-off that voters face.",
    "Advances in Machine Learning for Big Data have made such granular predictions a foundational feature of the modern polling industry.",
    "However, the potential democratic gains they convey should also be assessed and accounted for.",
    "In the next sections, we will highlight the tangible benefits of granular predictions in terms of enhancing democratic choice.",
    "Our view is that the privacy risks associated with the publication of granular predictions are real, but outweighed by the gain in public knowledge, which we deem significant."
  ],
